name: Follow Up Remarks
query:
select 
    ev.reference_name as "Document Link:Link/Event:120",
    ev.content as "Description:Data:440",
    DATE(ev.communication_date) as "Date:Date:120",
    ep.link_name as "Lead:Link/Lead::150"
from `tabCommunication` ev, `tabCommunication Link` ep 
where ep.link_name = 'CRM-LEAD-2019-00038';
